                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0False Doctrine.",
                        "start": 131,
                        "end": 150
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "Speaking lies in hypocrisy; having their conscience seared with a hot iron;",
                "footnotes": [
