                        "end": 19
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Abstain.",
                        "start": 39,
                        "end": 46
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Food; Word of Wisdom.",
                        "start": 52,
                        "end": 57
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "D&C 49:19.",
                        "start": 74,
                        "end": 81
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "D&C 89:11 (11\u201313).",
                        "start": 102,
                        "end": 114
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 21,
                        "end": 35
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "For every creature of God is good, and nothing to be refused, if it be received with thanksgiving:",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "GR\u00a0creation.",
                        "start": 10,
                        "end": 18
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "Gen. 1:31.",
                        "start": 29,
                        "end": 33
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Thanksgiving.",
                        "start": 85,
                        "end": 97
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 26,
                        "end": 28
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "For it is sanctified by the word of God and prayer.",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "If thou put the brethren in remembrance of these things, thou shalt be a good minister of Jesus Christ, nourished up in the words of faith and of good doctrine, whereunto thou hast attained.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "GR\u00a0which thou hast followed closely.",
                        "start": 161,
                        "end": 189
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "But refuse profane and old wives' fables, and exercise thyself rather unto godliness.",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 63,
                        "end": 69
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "For bodily exercise profiteth little: but godliness is profitable unto all things, having promise of the life that now is, and of that which is to come.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "GR\u00a0a little while.",
                        "start": 30,
                        "end": 36
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "Luke 12:31. TG\u00a0Godliness.",
                        "start": 42,
                        "end": 51
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "This is a faithful saying and worthy of all acceptation.",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 5,
                        "end": 7
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "For therefore we both labour and suffer reproach, because we trust in the living God, who is the Saviour of all men, specially of those that believe.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Labor.",
                        "start": 22,
                        "end": 28
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Reproach.",
                        "start": 40,
                        "end": 48
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Trust in God.",
                        "start": 61,
                        "end": 66
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Jesus Christ, Atonement through; Jesus Christ, Savior.",
                        "start": 97,
                        "end": 104
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Faith.",
                        "start": 141,
                        "end": 148
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "These things command and teach.",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "Let no man despise thy youth; but be thou an example of the believers, in word, in conversation, in charity, in spirit, in faith, in purity.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "1\u00a0Cor. 16:11 (10\u201311).",
                        "start": 11,
                        "end": 18
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Example; Priesthood, Qualifying for.",
                        "start": 45,
                        "end": 52
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "GR\u00a0conduct, behavior.",
                        "start": 83,
                        "end": 95
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Chastity; Purity; Virtue.",
                        "start": 133,
                        "end": 139
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "Till I come, give attendance to reading, to exhortation, to doctrine.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Study.",
                        "start": 32,
                        "end": 39
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "Neglect not the gift that is in thee, which was given thee by prophecy, with the laying on of the hands of the presbytery.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Priesthood, Magnifying Callings within.",
                        "start": 0,
                        "end": 7
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0God, Gifts of; Stewardship; Talents.",
                        "start": 16,
                        "end": 20
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "1\u00a0Tim. 1:18. TG\u00a0Prophecy.",
                        "start": 62,
                        "end": 70
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Priesthood, Authority; Priesthood, Ordination.",
                        "start": 81,
                        "end": 87
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Hands, Laying on of.",
                        "start": 98,
                        "end": 103
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "GR\u00a0elders.",
                        "start": 111,
                        "end": 121
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "Meditate upon these things; give thyself wholly to them; that thy profiting may appear to all.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Meditation.",
                        "start": 0,
                        "end": 8
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "GR\u00a0progress, advancement.",
                        "start": 66,
                        "end": 75
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "GR\u00a0be manifest in all.",
                        "start": 80,
                        "end": 93
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [
                    {
                        "type": "paper-page-number",
                        "data": 1510
                    }
                ],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "Take heed unto thyself, and unto the doctrine; continue in them: for in doing this thou shalt both save thyself, and them that hear thee.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "James 5:20 (19\u201320); D&C 101:39 (39\u201340).",
